Deployment Plan

- Prerequisites:  Digital Ocean Account.  All your code committed to git/github.  A domain you want to use for your site.
- Creat a WarpSpeed account.  Use coupon code gocodeup
- Add Digital Ocean API Key to WarpSpeed Account
- Add public key to WarpSpeed Account
- Create a server
- Create a site
- Deploy your code


#Side Topics

- Ways people hosts websites
- Ways people deploy code
- What is an API key?
- What is this public key business?
- Async Processing.
- DNS
- Known hosts

Digital Ocean is a virtual private server provider.